HEADWORD: Plaited
<hw>Plait"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Folded; doubled over; braided;
figuratively, involved; intricate; artful.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Time shall unfold what <qex>plaited</qex> cunning hides.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Plaiter</ent>⟦br⟧
